title: Best of The Dan Patrick Show: 02/12/2021
itunes:title: Best of The Dan Patrick Show: 02/12/2021
description:
Jason Smith and Doug Gottlieb react to breaking news that J.J. Watt has been released by the Houston Texans. They speak with Tampa Bay Buccaneers center A.Q. Shipley about winning a championship in his final season playing in the NFL. Plus, they talk about whether or not it is too early to judge the Texans' head-scratching moves.
